public long getDataFilterID(java.lang.String dataTypeName,
                            java.lang.String dataFilterName)
Query the dataFilterID with dataTypeName and dataFilterNames. This method is caching the result into filterIDMap.

Parameters:
dataTypeName - is name of the dataType it filters on
dataFilterName - is name of the dataFilter
Returns:
filterID that matches dataTypeName and dataFilterName or -1 if no match
